{
  "stem": "8775.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that meant that you could not get, you couldn't take in more people to the first year class than there were Jewish people in front of you in the prior class.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So since there was nobody in the prior year, I was not accepted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father furiously looked around to see what could be done so I would be enrolled in a gymnasium, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he found a school, a private Calvinist school, which was named from the-- Hungary's regent, Admiral Horthy, spelled H-O-R-T-H-Y.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was not in the city of Szolnok.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was like, 35 kilometers or 50 kilometers east from Szolnok.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he enrolled me over there, and I had to go once a year, sitting in the classes for like, a week.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then around June, I went in with my tutor, who was my first cousin, and passed all of the written and oral tests.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that time, I started noticing, of course-- not only from the Numerus Clausus, but also from the atmosphere of the street, how things have changed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Thugs started to approach me in the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They started to start fights, started trouble on the streets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Also on the ice skating rink, they, they would purposely block me so I would fall.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they started laughing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They thought it was hilarious.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And not only with me, but with other Jewish children, they did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They called you names, dirty names, and dirty Jew, what have you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They always made fun of your nose, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have a Jewish nose, or what have you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You were afraid to-- pretty much to show up on the street, because of these thugs, who were perhaps, belong to parties.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
